{"tid":484363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【2018世界盃】ViuTV免費播19場世界盃 揭幕戰、4強同決賽有得睇","createTime":"2017-11-30T04:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T04:52:09.000Z","uid":73262,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6f0d98e600dc906167837e855b1a9c1a39916e81","tid":484363,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T04:28:16.000Z","msg":"電訊盈科（008）旗下Now TV及ViuTV將於香港獨家播放俄羅斯2018年FIFA世界盃，揭幕戰將於明年6月14日舉行，7月15日決賽。俄羅斯世界盃播映權原本由樂視去年奪得。<br />\nNow TV獨家直播全部64場賽事，ViuTV則播送19場賽事，包括揭幕戰、兩場準決賽及決賽。明晚（12月1日）Now TV、ViuTV會率先於10時55分、11時直播俄羅斯舉行的分組抽籤儀式。<br />\n[蘋果財經，關心你飯碗]<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171130&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=57523130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171130%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D57523130&d=AbwvgHSBefXHsD12AOHk7xOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=0ebc17a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171130%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D57523130&h=025ee666\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171130&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=57523130</a>"},{"pid":"e8e5851022d801467b70701759a2cad137e65c62","tid":484363,"uid":160581,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T04:51:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9072343dec2e06ede0b714e5ce79bf3c5cb5b4a","tid":484363,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T04:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56092efe8e7f08ada345eabe1ef637597340c71e","tid":484363,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T04:52:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}